```

### Run Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
pytest

# With coverage
pytest --cov=wave_view --cov-report=html

# Run specific test file
pytest tests/test_basic.py -v
```

### Code Quality

```bash
# Format code
black src/ tests/

# Sort imports
isort src/ tests/

# Lint code
flake8 src/ tests/

# Type checking
mypy src/
```

